cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on object recognition using deep neural networks in the context of automotive radar technology. This makes it likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of machine learning and transfer learning suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
